    <briefdescription>
<para>Data structure for external accelerometer data. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This structure is used to represent the accelerometer data that can be collected from an external accelerometer and then fed into the MAX32664C sensor hub. It contains the x, y, and z acceleration values. This structure is only used when the external accelerometer is enabled. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
